No, I don't think it's even possible for that family to exist.

524
00:31:23,582 --> 00:31:26,518
We assigned a new person to St. Fiona's celebrity.

525
00:31:26,585 --> 00:31:28,520
Well, I'm the commander.

526
00:31:28,587 --> 00:31:31,523
At the very least, I'll raise your skills to an intermediate level.

527
00:31:31,590 --> 00:31:33,092
(Nagasaka) Yes.

528
00:31:35,594 --> 00:31:39,965
We will now begin an emergency caesarean section for placental abruption.

529
00:31:40,032 --> 00:31:42,034
Female. (Nurse) Yes.

530
